nation\r\n    for those looking to study MBBS in Uzbekistan. With the assistance of MBBS Consultants in Uzbekistan, students can\r\n    pursue direct admission to institutions like the Andijan State Medical Institute, fostering academic and\r\n    professional growth in this vibrant city.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    Embark on Your Medical Journey Today With Andijan State Medical Institute, studying MBBS in Uzbekistan has never been easier. Our commitment to academic\r\n    excellence, state-of-the-art facilities, and comprehensive support ensure that you\'ll receive the highest quality\r\n    education while pursuing your medical degree. Ready to take the next step? Contact our MBBS consultants in\r\n    Uzbekistan and start your journey towards a successful medical career today!\r\n</p>', '2025-08-29 07:23:33', '2025-09-01 06:50:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
