(20, '1756724945_f0d3babadd529335e5d5.png', 'Unlocking Boundless Horizons: Fargana Medical Institute of Public Health', '<h2>\r\n    Introduction to Fargana Medical Institute of Public Health\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    Nestled in the heart of Uzbekistan, Fargana Medical Institute of Public Health has earned its reputation as a\r\n    premier destination for students aspiring to study MBBS in Uzbekistan. Established with a commitment to excellence\r\n    in medical education, the institute has become a hub for global learning and cross-cultural exchange.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<table>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Established\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            1991\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            location\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Fergana, Uzbekistan\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            University type\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Public\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Course\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            MBBS (5.8 years with 1 year Internship)\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Class Commencement\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            September & October every year\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Eligibility\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            50% in PCB + Online Test or Interview\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            IELTS/TOFEL\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            N/A\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Language\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            English\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Affiliations and Recognition\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Affiliated with Fergana State University Medical Centre for comprehensive practical exposure.\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Recognized by the World Health Organization (WHO) and the National Medical Council (NMC) for international\r\n        standards.\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Why Choose Fergana Medical Institute?\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Workplace Preparation:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Committed to equipping students for fast-paced healthcare challenges.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Interactive Learning:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Engaging methodologies for a dynamic and enriching educational experience.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Latest Technologies:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Integration of cutting-edge technologies to prepare students for the global workforce.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Global Recognition:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Welcoming foreign students and scientists, fostering a diverse and intellectually stimulating environment.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Affordability:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Affordable fees and a reasonable cost of living, ensuring accessibility to quality medical education.\r\n    </p>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Courses Offered\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    Fargana Medical Institute of Public Health offers a comprehensive array of courses, providing students with a solid\r\n    foundation in the field of medicine. The flagship programme, MBBS, is designed to meet international standards and\r\n    is recognized worldwide. The institute is committed to nurturing skilled healthcare professionals equipped with the\r\n    latest knowledge and practical skills.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<h3>\r\n    Fee Structure\r\n</h3><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    One of the key factors attracting students to study MBBS in Uzbekistan is the cost-effective nature of educa