n Russia journey.\r\n    If you are considering embarking on your medical education in Russia, Ulyanovsk State University definitely warrants\r\n    your exploration.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>\r\n        Remember, you can directly connect with MBBS Consultants in Russia who can guide you through the entire\r\n        application process, making your journey to a rewarding MBBS in Russia at USU smooth and hassle-free.\r\n    </b>\r\n</p>', '2025-09-03 05:40:21', '2025-09-03 06:28:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(23, '1756881056_56461b72f057efe6aa0b.png', 'Embark on Your Medical Journey: Unveiling Shymkent State Medical University', '<h2>\r\n    Introduction to Shymkent State Medical University:\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    Established in 1997, SSMU boasts a rich history of academic excellence and innovation. Recognized by prominent\r\n    bodies like the World Health Organization (WHO), the Medical Council of India (MCI), and many more, the university\r\n    is committed to providing its students with a comprehensive and globally recognized medical education.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<table>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Institute name\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Shymkent State Medical University\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Location\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Shymkent, Kazakhstan\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Nationality\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Both international and national allowed\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            NEET\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Yes, required\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Courses Duration\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            6 year including 1 year internship\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Authorisation\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Authorized by WHO, MCI and NMC\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Affiliated with\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Ministry of Education and Science of the Republic of Kazakhstan\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Basic Criteria\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            10+2 with 60% marks is required\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            IELTS/TOFEL\r\n        </td>\r\n   