(24, '1756901055_b0603f1f7bb3950a061d.png', 'Kuban State Medical University: Your Gateway to a Fulfilling MBBS Journey in Russia', '<h2>\r\n    A Legacy of Excellence: Unveiling Kuban State Medical University:\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    Established in 1920, KSMU boasts a rich history of nurturing talented medical professionals. With over a century of\r\n    experience, the university has earned a reputation for academic excellence and is recognized by leading medical\r\n    councils globally, including the Medical Council of India (MCI). This recognition ensures graduates can pursue MBBS\r\n    in Russia and pave the way for a successful medical career in various countries.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<table>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            University Recognitions\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            ECFMG, FAIMER, GMC PLAB, WDOMS, AMC, NMC (erstwhile MCI), etc.\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Courses\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            MBBS (6 Years with Internship)\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Eligibility Criteria\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Qualified Class 12 with 50% marks in PCB\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            NEET Required\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            yes\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Intake Period\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            September\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            Language\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            English\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Courses Offered: Embark on Your Medical Path\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    KSMU offers a comprehensive MBBS in Russia program, spanning five years and designed to equip students with the\r\n    knowledge, skills, and values required to excel in the medical field. The program covers a diverse range of\r\n    subjects, including:\r\n</p><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Anatomy\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Physiology\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Biochemistry\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Pathology\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Pharmacology\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Community Medicine\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Internal Medicine\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Surgery\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Pediatrics\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Obstetrics & Gynecology\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        And more\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Fee Structure:\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<table>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <th>\r\n            years\r\n        </th>\r\n        <th>\r\n            Tution fees(USD)\r\n        </th>\r\n        <th>\r\n            Medical insurance(USD)\r\n        </th>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            1st year\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            4500\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            200\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            2nd year\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            3800\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            200\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            3rd year\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            3800\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            200\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            4th year\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            3800\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            200\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            5th year\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            3800\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            200\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td>\r\n            6th year\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            3800\r\n        </td>\r\n        <td>\r\n            200\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table><br>\r\n<h3>\r\n    Affordable Education: Making Your Dream a Reality\r\n</h3><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    KSMU is renowned for its affordable MBBS in Russia fees. Compared to the high costs associated with studying\r\n    medicine in many other countries, KSMU presents a financially viable option for students from diverse backgrounds.\r\n    This accessibility allows students to pursue their medical aspirations without facing significant financial burdens,\r\n    making it a truly democratizing force in the realm of medical education.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Dissecting the MBBS in Russia Syllabus: A Balanced Approach:\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    The MBBS in Russia syllabus at KSMU adheres to the highest international standards. The meticulously crafted\r\n    curriculum incorporates:\r\n</p><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            In-depth Theoretical Foundation:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Through lectures and discussions, students gain a strong foundation in various medical disciplines.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Hands-on Practical Training:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Laboratories, clinical rotations in affiliated hospitals, and simulated scenarios equip students with practical\r\n        skills essential for real-world medical practice.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Continuous Evaluation:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Regular assessments, including examinations and practical evaluations, ensure students are progressing well and\r\n        mastering the required competencies.\r\n    </p>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<h3>\r\n    Faculty: Mentors Guiding Your Medical Journey\r\n</h3><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    KSMU houses a distinguished faculty comprising highly qualified professors, doctors of science, and experienced\r\n    medical practitioners. Their expertise and dedication ensure students receive top-notch guidance and mentorship\r\n    throughout their academic journey. Many faculty members are multilingual, facilitating seamless communication and\r\n    learning for international students.\r\n</p><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Accommodation: A Home Away from Home\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p>\r\n    KSMU provides comfortable on-campus hostels catering specifically to international students. These hostels offer:\r\n</p><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Shared Accommodation:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Rooms are oftentimes shared between 2-3 students, fostering a sense of community and cultural exchange.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Essential Amenities:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Each room is equipped with essential amenities like Wi-Fi, electricity, and water supply.\r\n    </p><br>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Supportive Environment:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        The hostels provide a safe and secure environment conducive to studying and making lifelong friendships.\r\n    </p>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Placement: Stepping into a Successful Career\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n        KSMU boasts a well-established network of hospitals and medical institutions across Russia.\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        The university actively assists its graduates in securing MBBS in Russia placements, ensuring a smooth\r\n        transition into professional practice.\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Graduates are also eligible to take national licensing exams to practice medicine in their home countries after\r\n        completing their studies and fulfilling specific regulations.\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<h2>\r\n    Advantages of Studying MBBS at Kuban State Medical University:\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <b>\r\n        <li>\r\n            Internationally recognized degree:\r\n        </li>\r\n    </b>\r\n    <p>\r\n        The MBBS in Russia degree from KSMU is recognized global